        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(feishu): attach quoted media to agent context",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Preserve raw Feishu message content when fetching quoted/replied messages.\n- Reuse the existing Feishu media resolver to download media from quoted file/image/audio/video/media/sticker/post messages.\n- Attach downloaded quoted media to the agent context (`MediaPath`, `MediaPaths`, `MediaTypes`) while keeping the quoted text fallback (`ReplyToBody`).\n\n## Why\n\nWhen a user replies to a Feishu file message and mentions the bot, the current inbound message is text while the file lives on the quoted parent message. Previously OpenClaw only parsed that parent as text (for example `[file message]`), so the agent never received a local media path and could not inspect the file.\n\n## Tests\n\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.extension-feishu.config.ts extensions/feishu/src/send.test.ts extensions/feishu/src/bot.test.ts`\n- `pnpm lint:extensions -- extensions/feishu/src/bot.ts extensions/feishu/src/send.ts extensions/feishu/src/types.ts extensions/feishu/src/bot.test.ts extensions/feishu/src/send.test.ts`\n",
        "branch": "feishu-quoted-media-context",
